description: This file implements the functions related to an HTTP simple proxy's behavior, including handling request and response headers and bodies, as well as completion signals. The functions are mostly placeholders that currently do nothing but return success status.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS HttpSpoPbcRecvReqHeaders(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hSession,ANSC_HANDLE hMessage)
methods.description: Handles incoming request headers for the proxy; currently a placeholder that returns success.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS HttpSpoPbcRecvReqBody(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hSession,ANSC_HANDLE hMessage)
methods.description: Handles incoming request body for the proxy; currently a placeholder that returns success.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS HttpSpoPbcReqComplete(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hSession)
methods.description: Signifies completion of request processing; currently a placeholder that returns success.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS HttpSpoPbcRecvRepHeaders(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hSession,ANSC_HANDLE hMessage)
methods.description: Handles incoming response headers for the proxy; currently a placeholder that returns success.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS HttpSpoPbcRecvRepBody(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hSession,ANSC_HANDLE hMessage)
methods.description: Handles incoming response body for the proxy; currently a placeholder that returns success.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS HttpSpoPbcRepComplete(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hSession)
methods.description: Signifies completion of response processing; currently a placeholder that returns success.
